Name: Project Rhombus
About the game: Project Rhombus is a rhythm-based casual action game that combines exciting electronic music with stylish flat design. Hold on as long as possible, blocking the oncoming arrows moving to the beat. Features Music with sensual beat Minimalistic graphics Easy to learn, quite hard to master 100% free! in honor of Toby Fox
